      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EQUITY (6) has a strong winning strike-rate here with three wins and a placing from seven tries. Recorded a 8 length win (21.82) in a P5 last time at this track. Expected to go close. SPRING FLICK (8) was prominent early from the tricky draw and stalked the lead before levelling up to score (21.99) at this track in a P5 over 390m. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Likely to be in the finish. CUPOLA (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.36) at this track behind PROFESSOR SAXON in a P5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. FIRE UP SHAZAM (7) is a last-start placegetter here at this trip - worth considering.",
